=head2 block_topic_list_of_future_links

 block_topic_list_of_future_links {topic}

Shows a block with a list of links to stories with
a date in the future.

=cut
<div class = 'future_stories_list'>
{-if|{-is_topic_editor|$0}|
	<ul>
	<li>{-link_to_new_story|$0}</li>
	{-foreach|{-stories_by_date|$0|0|0|{-date}||1}|
		<li>\{-story_date\|%y/%m/%d\|\$0\|\$1\} - \{-link_to_story_with_edit\|\$0\|\$1\}</li>
	}
	</ul>
}
</div>
